Package suncertify.business

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RemoteSubcontractorService
    The remote business service implementation of SubcontractorService.
    SubcontractorService
    The SubcontractorService interface contains all business functionality of the application.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultSubcontractorService
    DefaultSubcontractorService is the main business service implementation of SubcontractorService.
    RMIRemoteSubcontractorService
    RMIRemoteSubcontractorService is an RMI implementation of the remote business service interface RemoteSubcontractorService.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ServicesException
    ServicesException is the superclass of all exceptions in the suncertify.business package.
    SubcontractorAlreadyBookedException
    The class SubcontractorAlreadyBookedException should be used when a Subcontractor is not able to be booked on the server if it is already booked by another client
    SubcontractorNotFoundException
    The class SubcontractorNotFoundException should be used when a Subcontractor is not found on the server
